  <article class="about__service">
    <header class="header__service">
      <h4 class="title__service">
        Style Consultation
      </h4>
    </header>

    <p class="service">
      A one-on-one conversation either in person, or over the phone.<br>
      This is a time for us to determine your true style, outline your needs, wants, and budget, and put together a game plan to bring clarity to the process.
    </p>
  </article>

  <article class="about__service">
    <header class="header__service">
      <h4 class="title__service">
        Wardrobe / Closet Consultation
      </h4>
    </header>

    <p class="service">
      An in home, hands on assessment of your current clothing options.<br>
      After outlining your needs in our Style Consultation, we can get down to executing our plan!
    </p>

    <p class="sub-service"><span class="title__sub-service"><em>Purging:​</em></span> Closet purging is a necessary step that I see all too often for clients who have difficulty getting dressed. This step can sometimes be difficult to accomplish on your own, simply because we all have sentimental connections to items, which can limit our ability to let go. Together we will go through and establish which pieces are no longer serving a purpose for you, and then decide whether to donate or consign.
    </p>

    <p class="sub-service"><span class="title__sub-service"><em>Wardrobing​:</em></span> Outfitting can be a major benefit for clients who have busy lifestyles and just don’t have the time to think about assembling a cohesive outfit every morning. It’s also a great way to help those who want a little guidance in improving their current favorite ensembles, or a push to step out of their box completely with something new.<br>
    <br>
    This step can be done in your closet together if your schedule permits, or I can easily prepare some choices and present them to you for review in home or at a store. I will organize a picture book of head to toe outfits for all occasions (work, vacation, date night, event dressing, etc.) to make dressing a stress free and confidence boosting experience.
    </p>

    <p class="sub-service">
      <span class="title__sub-service"><em>Closet Organization:</em></span>​ Sometimes the issue can be as simple as your closet not being organized correctly to help you get dressed efficiently. This is usually an easy fix that just about everyone can benefit from to transform the experience of getting dressed from overwhelming, to stress free and enjoyable.
    </p>
  </article>

