  <article class="about__service">
    <header class="header__service">
      <h4 class="title__service">
        Personal Shopping
      </h4>
    </header>

    <p class="service">
      If we determine that you need some new pieces to fill in the holes in your wardrobe, then shopping is the next step! This can be done with or without you, and we can shop locally, out of town, or online. These specifics can be established in your consultation, and will be tailored to suit both your style, as well as your lifestyle goals. After shopping we will have a fitting to decide what works, what doesn’t, what needs to be tailored, and what will work best into your current wardrobe.
    </p>
  </article>

  <article class="about__service">
    <header class="header__service">
      <h4 class="title__service">
        Travel Packing
      </h4>
    </header>

    <p class="service">
      We all have difficulty packing, and most women (as well as more than a few men!) are chronic over-packers. I will help you determine the pieces that will allow for maximum versatility on any trip, and I’ll help eliminate the time and stress of packing and organizing your suitcase, so that you can focus your pre-trip time on more important things. Whether it’s a business trip or a beach vacation, your wardrobe will be personalized according to destination, weather forecast, and any planned events on your itinerary. Your included outfits will be pictured and outlined in order to take all of the deliberation and stress out of getting dressed, and keep your attention where it matters.
    </p>
  </article>

  <article class="about__service" id="service-packages">
    <header class="header__service">
      <h4 class="title__service">
        Packages
      </h4>
    </header>
    <p class="service">
      I offer combination packages that are tailored to your individual needs, determined during your consultation. For example, you may need assistance packing, but also need a few new outfits for your trip. I can combine these services and offer them at a packaged price based on your specific needs.
    </p>
  </article>
  <article class="about__service" id="service-packages">
