      </h4>
    </header>
    <p class="service">
      Curated shopping trips are the perfect way to celebrate birthdays, anniversaries, new motherhood, or just a great excuse to spend time with friends and family.<br>
      <br>
      I currently offer trips to Atlanta, Nashville, and New York, with a couple of new exciting locations coming in 2019! Depending on your budget and desires, we can put together a day trip to Atlanta or a fully curated long weekend in New York.
    </p>
  </article>
